#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/blending_modes/lighten.rst:407
msgid "This blending mode is called \"Tint (IFS Illusions)\" in English."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/blending_modes/lighten.rst:409
msgid ""
"Basically, the blending mode only ends in shades of tints. This means that "
"it's very useful for painting light colors while still in the range of tints."
msgstr ""
"基本的に、この合成モードはかすかな色にしかなりません。つまり色のある範囲に明"
"るい色を塗っていくときにとても便利です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/blending_modes/lighten.rst:414
